Description: Simulate correlated multi-endpoint clinical trial data using a Gaussian
    copula approach. This package provides tools to generate realistic patient-level
    datasets with configurable treatment effects and covariance structures. It supports
    multiple endpoint types (continuous, binary, count, and time-to-event) across
    multiple treatment arms.
